  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Barista / Tearista",
  "description": "<h1><strong>Level Up: Baristas &amp; Tearistas Wanted!</strong> </h1>\n<p><strong>Ditch the boring desk job.</strong> We're looking for the next wave of <strong>Baristas</strong> and <strong>Tearistas</strong> to join our team and serve up serious flavours. No corporate jargon, just great coffee, amazing tea, and even better vibes.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We believe the best beverages are made by people who truly enjoy them. <strong>Drinking coffee and/or tea is required</strong>, and if you love both, that's a huge bonus! </p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>No experience? No stress.</strong> We're hiring for attitude and potential. If you love the grind (literally) and are ready to learn, we'll teach you the rest. What We Offer:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Salary:</strong> $2,000 - $2,500 per month</li>\n  <li><strong>Work Schedule:</strong> 5.5-day work week (More life outside of work!)</li>\n  <li><strong>Location:</strong> Conveniently located with <strong>easy access to the MRT</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Growth:</strong> Real career progression. We’re not gatekeeping your future.</li>\n  <li><strong>Experience:</strong> <strong>Zero required.</strong> Seriously. We provide comprehensive training!</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<h3>What You'll Be Doing:</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Crafting delicious, high-quality coffee and tea beverages.</li>\n  <li>Someone who can keep the energy high and the drinks flowing.</li>\n  <li>A team player who can jump in and help out.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<h3>How to Apply:</h3>\n<p>If you're eager to learn, have a great attitude, and love what we brew, we want to hear from you! <strong>Stop scrolling. Drop us your CV today.</strong> Seriously, what are you waiting for?</p>\n<p>teadot@tlefood.com / contact 91990467</p>",
